    public abstract class AbstractUniProtIdentifierMappingParser<ResultType>
extends AbstractHTMLParser<ResultType>
    This is a clumsy parser for the response provided by the UniProt ID mapping service. Due to redirection and potentially malformed URLs that contains white spaces, this is required. Automatic redirection will not work here and needs manual intervention. Do not use for other purposes.
